content.p: The Knowledge Exchange and Impact Awards celebrate impact arising from all research disciplines across the University of Nottingham. Awards across all five faculties were recognised at a formal awards evening on 22 November 2018. The winners can be found here. Find out about the 2018 Knowledge Exchange and Impact awards.
